# Project README

This repository contains code related to clock functions.

## Header Inclusion

`headers.h` contains clock functions and should be included anywhere these functions are used in your project.

## Time Retrieval

To retrieve the current time, call:

```c
getClk();
```

## Building and Running

You can use the provided Makefile to build and run your project.

### Compilation

To compile your project, use the following command:

```bash
make
```

### Running

To run your project, use the following command:

```bash
make run
```

### Adding Files

If you add a new file to your project, remember to include it in the build section of the Makefile.

- Ensure that each line in the Makefile starts with a tab character, as it is the syntax for Makefile.
